~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : finger                                    ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : finger [<username>@<site>/-r]

   This command allows the admin to check on users email address to see
   if the users exists on the site listed in the .accreq

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : whois, nslookup, accreq
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
